metadata.name: Trapper Keeper
metadata.description:
Sometimes you just gotta write it down. All the thoughts in your head — the ones that don’t make sense. Putting them down on the page helps you piece them together, later. Even if it’s just a doodle, ‘cause sometimes the words just... aren’t there? This binder is full of ‘em. Brainstorms, drawings, journal entries, daydreams... bad poetry haha. It’s hard to imagine someone else reading this. Even harder to imagine them understanding.



Utility

 - Access to the Abel Okugawa Twitter Community

 - Token-gated access to the Abel Okugawa Web3 Vault Site with links and info

 - Invites to live talks and interviews



Credits:

 - Abel Okugawa - Producer
